{"tid":1028571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日蔡英文教你英文：Comment","createTime":"2019-02-19T14:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T17:39:42.000Z","uid":226955,"like":95,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd3a2593a968c9ee2ff2e85193dc47dbf6276b9","tid":1028571,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"蔡英文Facebook：<br />\n<br />\nComment是一個常在新聞英文中出現的詞彙，提供例句給各位同學參考：<br />\n<br />\n🔺名詞的用法：<br />\nPresident Tsai Ing-wen rejects Beijing leader&rsquo;s unfriendly <span style=\"color: red;\">comments</span>.<br />\n蔡英文總統拒絕北京領導人不友善的言論。<br />\n<br />\n🔺動詞的用法：<br />\nAs there is no censorship in Taiwan, Brother Caramel can freely <span style=\"color: red;\">comment</span> on public affairs.<br />\n台灣沒有審查制度，焦糖哥哥可以自由地評論各種公共議題。<br />\n<br />\n這樣大家都學會了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n#言論自由<br />\n#跟英文一起學英文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXyEW0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXyEW0y.png&h=9d17c5cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ade70bb3d9e5edad9bd2942260aeeaf8550e55f5","tid":1028571,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59eebe51135d3847a4645691d2605fa29b5dc015","tid":1028571,"uid":103156,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:04:21.000Z","msg":"No comment."},{"pid":"1ada3fd665fae8d2c3aea4b42ea4f462eb943561","tid":1028571,"uid":143499,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:04:26.000Z","msg":"幾大量<br />\n<br />\n畀著Chi-Na維尼熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間學校應該剷平咗"},{"pid":"27c611286e57f684fbce6e6870273786ade89d85","tid":1028571,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:11:15.